➜英特尔独显终于来了！华硕这款笔记本首发
http://www.sohu.com/a/425951422_223764	8361
<p>[PConline 资讯]<span>近期，华硕将发布了一款全新翻转本</span><span>“</span><span>VivoBook Flip 14 TP470EZ</span><span>”。</span><span>从流出的产品信息来看，其搭配了</span><span>Intel DG1</span><span>独立显卡，这也是全球首款。</span></p>
<p><span>据了解，</span><span>该</span><span>产品采用</span><span>Intel Tiger Lake 11</span><span>代酷睿平台，处理器可选</span><span>i7-1165G7</span><span>、</span><span>i5-1135G7</span><span>，搭配显卡描述为</span><span>“</span><span>First Intel Discrete Graphics</span><span>”</span><span>，。</span><span>从其他媒体曝光的数据来看，</span><span>该</span><span>独立显卡有</span><span>96</span><span>个执行单元、</span><span>768</span><span>个核心，</span><span>并且</span><span>搭配</span><span>4GB</span><span>独立显存。</span><span>内存则是</span><span>8/16GB LPDDR4X-4266，可以更好发挥整机性能。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201020/b3e3b5bc271d44af9f49137272860a2f.jpeg" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201020/396575cda5bb4abfb443ad3c53a4eeb7.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>据了解，</span><span>这是</span><span>Intel</span><span>历史上第三次冲击独立显卡了</span><span>：</span><span>1998</span><span>年的</span><span>i740</span><span>昙花一现，十多年前的</span><span>Larrabee</span><span>胎死腹中</span><span>。随着十一代酷睿的推出和</span><span>Xe</span><span>集成显卡的优秀发挥（从测试来看已经达到了</span><span>M</span><span>X</span><span>250</span><span>显卡的水平）。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201020/bcfe3c8b417e4cf9b3638ed344d33dd8.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>也就是说，在接下来的轻薄本市场中，如果用户对显卡性能要求较高，可以选择搭载英特尔</span><span>Intel DG1</span><span>独立显卡的产品，而对图形处理性能要求不高的，则可以选择</span><span>Xe</span><span>核显的笔记本产品。</span></p>
<p><span>值得一提的是，目前入门级独显主要被英伟达MX系列显卡包揽，最新的入门级独显为MX450。</span></p>
